---
description: Mobile-first design constraints for field use
globs: "**/*.{tsx,css}"
alwaysApply: false
---

The primary device is a phone held by a technician on a job site.

- Camera must default to rear-facing: `facingMode: "environment"`
- Touch targets minimum 44x44px (WCAG 2.5.5)
- Font minimum 16px body text
- Use `100dvh` not `100vh` for full viewport height (handles mobile browser chrome)
- Test with Chrome DevTools mobile emulator before considering done
- No hover-only interactions — everything must work with touch
- Prefer bottom-anchored controls (thumb-friendly zone)
- Disable user-select and text zoom on the main session view
